VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT Invoke-Expression\s+["']?.*\$\w|iex\s+["']?.*\$\w
WHEN EXPR MISSING:Validate|Sanitize|allowlist|\[ValidateSet\]|\[ValidatePattern\]
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Invoke-Expression (iex) calls that include variable interpolation.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Invoke-Expression with Variable Input.
